### 2. Get All Customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/internal/customer/list
X-Client-Key: {{clientKey}}

### 3. Get Customer by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/internal/customer/{{customerId}}
X-Client-Key: {{clientKey}}

### 4. Update Customer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v1/internal/customer/{{customerId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Client-Key: {{clientKey}}

{
  "username": "testcustomer_updated",
  "name": "Test Customer Updated",
  "phone": "089876543210",
  "email": "updated@test.com",
  "address": "Updated Address 456",
  "password": "newpassword456",
  "profile_id": "{{profileId}}",
  "service_type": "pppoe",
  "billing_day": 15,
  "auto_suspension": false,
  "customer_notes": "Updated customer notes"
}

### 5. Ping Customer (One-time)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/internal/customer/{{customerId}}/ping
X-Client-Key: {{clientKey}}

### 6. Delete Customer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/internal/customer/{{customerId}}
X-Client-Key: {{clientKey}}